name: Tezos Postcards #1 "Welcome to Nice"
description: There will be 100 different Tezos Postcards total in 100 different locations. 20 of each card will be minted. This postcard features my original video and animation work while on a trip to Nice, France with my wife in 2020. This gentleman was pretty relaxed and soaking in the rays, unaware of the filmer above. All music, video, and artwork were done by the NFT creator Clipdad. This is a 600 x 338 MP4 Video. The song is "Haw Eye" by Clipdad.
